  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6607.3 sitting just below the GEX flip at 6608 in PIN regime, dealers are positioned as stabilizers and likely selling gamma into any push higher toward the massive 6605-6610 positive gamma wall (51M+ combined). The wall_break and gex_surge events with 64%+ gamma changes suggest we just pierced through a key level, but the heavy positive gamma concentration from 6605-6625 should act as significant resistance and cap upside momentum. Watch 6608 flip level closely - staying below keeps dealers in supportive mode, while a sustained break above shifts them to headwind sellers into the 6610-6620 gamma wall complex.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect the market to get capped near current levels with dealers selling any rally toward 6610-6620.",
